%% Multi-Agent Hierarchy - Agent Structure
%% Google Cloud Platform Style

graph TD
    subgraph "Root Layer"
        Root[🎯 Root Agent<br/>Model: Gemini 2.5 Pro<br/>Role: Coordinator & Router<br/>Error Handling: Always respond to user]
    end

    subgraph "Domain Specialists"
        Product[🛍️ Product Agent<br/>Model: Gemini 2.5 Flash<br/>Tools: 8<br/>• PreloadMemoryTool<br/>• search_products RAG<br/>• get_product_info default<br/>• get_all_saved_products_info multi]

        Order[📦 Order Agent<br/>Model: Gemini 2.5 Flash<br/>Tools: 5<br/>• PreloadMemoryTool<br/>• track_order<br/>• get_my_order_history<br/>• get_order_history<br/>• get_order_details]

        Billing[💳 Billing Agent<br/>Model: Gemini 2.5 Flash<br/>Tools: 8<br/>• PreloadMemoryTool<br/>• get_invoice<br/>• get_invoice_by_order_id<br/>• get_my_invoices<br/>• check_payment_status<br/>• get_my_payments<br/>• get_refundable_items<br/>• get_acceptable_refund_reasons<br/>Note: Refunds via refund_workflow only]
    end

    subgraph "Workflow Patterns"
        Sequential[🔄 Sequential Workflow<br/>Model: Gemini 2.5 Pro<br/>Refund Process with Validation Gates<br/>ONLY way to process refunds]

        subgraph "Sequential Steps"
            S1[1️⃣ Order Validator<br/>Gemini 2.5 Flash]
            S2[2️⃣ Eligibility Checker<br/>Gemini 2.5 Flash]
            S3[3️⃣ Refund Processor<br/>Gemini 2.5 Flash]
        end
    end

    Root -->|Products Query| Product
    Root -->|Orders Query| Order
    Root -->|Billing Query| Billing
    Root -->|Refund Request| Sequential

    Sequential --> S1
    S1 -->|✅ Valid| S2
    S2 -->|✅ Eligible| S3
    S3 -->|✅ Success| Root

    S1 -.->|❌ Invalid| Root
    S2 -.->|❌ Not Eligible| Root

